  "preload": [
    {
      "name": "docText",
      "unknown": false,
      "weight": 1.0,
      "values": null,
      "categories": null,
      "times": null,
      "approximate": false,
      "dataType": "textual",
      "sequence": null,
      "Value": "%% { canClaim.false %%Unfortunately you cannot claim for this flight delay.%% canClaim.false } %%%% { canClaim.true %%\nSend the following to your airline:\n\nTo whom it may concern, \n\nThank you for taking the time to read this letter. \nI am writing to you because my flight with you, number %% flightNumber %% was delayed. \n%% { claim.EU_LT1500 %%As the delay was over 3 hours and the flight distance within the EU was less than 1500KM I am entitled to 250 Euros in compensation.%%claim.EU_LT1500 } %%%% { claim.EU_GT1500 %%As the delay was over 3 hours and the flight distance within the EU was greater than 1500KM I am entitled to 400 Euros in compensation.%%claim.EU_GT1500 } %%%% { claim.EUNEU_LT1500 %%As the delay was over 3 hours and the flight distance with one terminus in the EU was less than 1500KM I am entitled to 250 Euros in compensation.%%claim.EUNEU_LT1500 } %%%% { claim.EUNEUGT_1500 %%As the delay was over 3 hours and the flight distance with one terminus in the EU was greater than 1500KM I am entitled to 400 Euros in compensation.%%claim.EUNEUGT_1500 } %%%% { claim.ENEUGT_3500 %%As the delay was over 4 hours and the flight distance with one terminus in the EU was greater than 3500KM I am entitled to 600 Euros in compensation.%%claim.ENEUGT_3500 } %%\n\nThe decision of the Court of Justice of the European Union in Tui & others v CAA confirmed the availability of compensation for delay as set out in the Sturgeon case. \nI am therefore seeking to apply EC Regulation 261/2004 to this delayed flight. \n\nFor these reasons I seek a reply to this letter within the next 14 days. \nAs I'm sure you are aware, simply having an address in the United Kingdom establishes jurisdiction for the UK courts. \nTherefore, if I do not receive a response, I intend to further my complaint including the possibility of involving the courts. \n\nI understand that in these situations, you may require additional information to verify my claim. Please find these details below: \n\nDate of flight: %% dateOfFlight %%\nTime of flight: %% timeOfFlight %%\nBooking reference: %% bookingRef %%\n\nI hope that you will accept my claim and arrange for the compensation to be sent promptly. \n\nYours sincerely, \n\n%% fullName %%\n%% canClaim.true } %%"
    },
    {
      "name": "cannotClaimText",
      "unknown": false,
      "weight": 1.0,
      "values": null,
      "categories": null,
      "times": null,
      "approximate": false,
      "dataType": "textual",
      "sequence": null,
      "Value": "Unfortunately you cannot claim for this delay according to EU rules."
    }
  ]
